title: Rename to NiubiDogeSwap
body:
Adding Doge to the name would help people discover NiubiSwap.

This is a fantastic, well-run project that deserves public interest. NiubiSwap provides high-yield farming and staking, rich features, and low-fee transactions that are backed by a progressive and communicative dev team.

Without public interest, this project may die. Devs can't live off crypto dreams.

Let's channel the massive public interest in DogeCoin to NiubiSwap.
